    R (>= 3.5.0)
Maintainer: Arnie Seong <akseong@uci.edu>
Description: Fundamental tools for mapping data to pitch and other sonic elements,
    usability of audio elements in RMarkdown workflows, and built-in functions
    for transforming several common visual plot types to audioplots.  
